item.title: The album debuted in the Top 3 of the Billboard 200 and spawned hit singles like ‘Heart Attack’ and ‘Neon Lights.’ It received praise from critics, mainly for Lovato’s vocals.

item.title: The song served as the lead single off ‘Younger Now’ and debuted with less than one day of tracking on the Billboard Hot 100. It went on to become her ninth Top 10 hit on the chart and is certified 2x Platinum in the US.
